parameters: \PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[6]"Ugh... Why am I dressed like this...?"

Told it was for the procedure, Kohane was firmly fixed to a
cross-shaped crucifix with both hands and feet. Her robe was
partially torn away, exposing her embarrassing parts to the
eyes of the scientist.

"Heh heh heh, it would be troublesome if you thrashed about
during the procedure. This is just a precaution... though
half of it is for my own amusement."
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[6]"(Ugh... Maybe I shouldn't have listened to him...)"

Regretting her decision to go along with the scientist's
suggestion, Kohane felt a bit of remorse.
"There's no need to be so scared... It will be over soon."
"Hmm, it seems to have taken hold successfully."

"This is an \C[2]Arousal Crest\C[0] that utilizes the
property of your spiritual power being released through
pleasure. It's designed to explosively increase your
spiritual power when your lust reaches its limit."
"Make the most of it, if you please."

<center>After continuously receiving H attacks from enemies,
when the lewdness level reaches 100%, you will transform
into \C[2]Arousal Crest Mode\C[0]. In \C[2]Arousal Crest
Mode\C[0], your magical attack power significantly
increases, but your MP will continuously decrease.
Additionally, your pleasure value (EP) will increase more,
making it easier to reach climax.</center>

<center>\C[2]Arousal Crest Mode\C[0] will automatically
deactivate after a certain period. Also, by using the item
"\C[2] \item[19]\C[0]", you can forcibly reduce the lewdness
level to 0.</center>
